  <div id="headerwrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-2">
          <p>My name is Sam Hotop and I have ideas.</p>
        </div>
      </div><!-- row -->
    </div><!-- container -->
  </div><!-- headerwrap -->

  <div id="aboutwrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-4" id="profileInfo">
          <img class="img-circle" src="/assets/samprofilepic.jpeg" width="120" height="130" alt="Icon">
          <h4>Sam Hotop</h4>
          <p>I'm glad <b>you</b> are here! I built this website as a platform through which to share my interests, passions, hobbies and ideas. I'm new to the dev side of software development, so if you have any feedback about the site's design or any bugs, please feel free to send me a message. I hope you find the content here fun and <b>engaging</b>.</p>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-offset-4 contact-form well well-sm">
            <form role="form">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactName">Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contactName" placeholder="Enter Name">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactEmail">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="contactEmail" placeholder="Email">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactMessage">Message</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Message for Sam"></textarea>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="blogwrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-2">
          <i class="fa fa-comment"><h4><%= link_to "BLOG", blog_path %></h4></i>
          <p>Life, technology, travel.  Find thoughts on these topics and more here. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- container -->
  </div>


  <div id="translationswrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-2">
          <i class="fa fa-language"><h4><%= link_to "TRANSLATIONS", translations_path %></h4></i>
          <p>Russian to English translations of news articles and other interesting content.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- container -->
  </div>

  <div id="musicwrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-2">
         <i class="fa fa-music"><h4><%= link_to "MUSIC", music_path %></h4></i>
         <p>I started my journey through Jazz guitar a couple years ago.  Hear some of the stuff I've been working on lately.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- container -->
  </div>


  <div id="projectswrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row centered">
        <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-2">
          <i class="fa fa-flask"><h4><%= link_to "PROJECTS", projects_path %></h4></i>
          <p>Video games, tools, random things I've been working on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- row -->
  </div><!-- container -->


